N+1 Query Problem (Very Important)

Example:

List<Account> accounts = repo.findAll();
accounts.forEach(a -> a.getTransactions());


Queries:

1 → Fetch accounts
N → Fetch transactions (for each account)


Total = N+1 queries

Fix
Use JOIN FETCH
@Query("SELECT a FROM Account a JOIN FETCH a.transactions")
List<Account> findAllWithTransactions();


OR

Use EntityGraph
@EntityGraph(attributePaths = "transactions")
List<Account> findAll();

